examples.en: He flatly denied ever having met the woman.
Mom flatly refused to go back into the hospital.
The article flatly contradicts their claims.
He seldom expresses any opinion one day without flatly contradicting it the next.
He slipped and landed flat on his back.
We asked for more time but they turned us down flat.
Coins are usually round and flat.
Her spokesperson flatly disclaimed the marriage rumor circulating in the press.
